Build

Build and manage interoperable and privacy-enabled smart contract applications that provide the Web3 foundation fit for financial institutions.

Extend

Extend the connections and applications driving market-level transformation across capital markets, banking, and payments.

Deliver new applications into a global ecosystem that includes 9 of the top 10 global investment banks, and enhance relationships with existing customers.

Discover previously impossible connections, enabled by Canton

 

Build or connect with enterprise-grade securities tokenization platforms covering the broadest range of assets, from government and corporate bonds to syndicated loans, commodities, and repo transactions. Issuers, investors, securities lenders, and post-trade service providers can seamlessly connect to rapidly drive value.

Break down the silos of marketplaces and systems to enable, create, and distribute the full range of digital assets that flow seamlessly through their lifecycle.

 

 

Investors and holders of digital assets need connected services to manage the post-trade lifecycle. Custodians, CSDs, and asset servicers provide digital safekeeping services and automation of post-trade and secondary market activities for the Canton Network.

Connect the dots to securely and confidently automate the asset lifecycle to shrink processing times, increase corporate-action transparency, and reduce operating costs and risks.

 

 

Seize first-mover advantage by providing the primary sources of digital cash on the Canton Network. Tokenize deposits or money market funds and extend as a network utility to make settlement optionality and atomic delivery versus payment a reality for digital assets on the network today. 

Capture the value of new payment flows across the Canton Network applications and put cash to work in new 24/7 markets.

 

 

The Canton Network connects the end-to-end digital asset lifecycle by synchronizing the flow of digital assets, post-trade services, and digital cash. Enable integrated support for the lending and re-use of digital assets, with applications ready to scale with the growth of tokenized securities. 

Unlock atomic transactions across counter-parties in securities lending, repo, and collateral management activities to lower operating cost and risks, increase collateral mobility, streamline compliance, and optimize capital.
